  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Vibe coding doesn't scale.",
      "checksum": "sha256:725e5f1421b90df6c9d7145f54c209fd0e5b93624928b4cf8925a01a15c83884",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 1.4860833333333334,
      "word_count": 4,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "It always ends in two thousand line files and agents hallucinating patterns.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c3374041d560f212964e200b07c2280f4632b503157ae8f8c7e812e7a8741110",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 4.179583333333333,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 4
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Here's the fix.",
      "checksum": "sha256:996d02807e9be86d9e1608310d4f7da06fcb14addcdae944ffb714db974863bd",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 1.161,
      "word_count": 3,
      "words_offset": 16
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "I ran a ninety minute workshop on this.",
      "checksum": "sha256:031dc61be4bad8f9054fbf83be7b5099638a151a7ab436872b060b3e89c56c35",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 2.0897916666666667,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 19
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Six strategies, no fluff.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7c64de6eb1c41644c622b8c6ad63fe2cb46c70be607aefb3eca5a237104dddec",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 1.4860833333333334,
      "word_count": 4,
      "words_offset": 27
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "They turn any messy codebase into something an agent can actually navigate.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9b50df4e2bfedc9ebabbcd7a8687cf550ce4087418831069d52aedd371ab130e",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.9009583333333335,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 31
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Ninety seven engineers in the room.",
      "checksum": "sha256:09ea750c98d4294d5a738c3f9ead622b0cb5df24ad500c45b793b46927733337",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 1.8575833333333334,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 43
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Real codebases.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dd491a9d1d2d4096557e9a823a1147cdd7600f049faf13d6c764d44b1bf64292",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 1.253875,
      "word_count": 2,
      "words_offset": 49
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "And one specific failure mode is killing most of them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:38ecdc4fa82ee5bbe91bae4d1d18ca1b8560998ee635855051cd3e876213a173",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 2.972166666666667,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 51
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "File size isn't the metric.",
      "checksum": "sha256:150a2cbb1ed46b3fd0770eb2d0d809dfc5de262c7d46af4c3deac5b6e7ecc32c",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 1.4860833333333334,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 61
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "A two thousand line file with three imports is fine.",
      "checksum": "sha256:daa1a7bc3b8992df1ca4b6518760712aa1018bced1f117a03adee3e6dfae275d",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792916666666666,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 66
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Coupling is what kills you.",
      "checksum": "sha256:580f3de3b19d3cead8a66e5366f565728e97cdc68d6d61624e3ce117f95c67d2",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 1.4860833333333334,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 76
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Six strategies.",
      "checksum": "sha256:933a5bbe76c1fdb4f1c656d2a22b545f125c3241ff032b5491bba25d6d6d4caa",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 1.161,
      "word_count": 2,
      "words_offset": 81
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "One \u2014 vertical slices.",
      "checksum": "sha256:93b4e25b375dc70455cbd8cb5214741dea3065833379ef98c087971f0aa1aec9",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 1.4860833333333334,
      "word_count": 4,
      "words_offset": 83
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Organize by feature, not by layer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a61df49da14d0967cdfcde3a8f962ddcbf4051fac07b5f4bbfe34a1c09737106",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 2.043375,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 87
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Two \u2014 brownfield day one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9ac7101253b752805adf8a4fcac3c0c2adcb31ff1122fa0de82bcf81524f08c5",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 1.439625,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 93
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Use sub-agents to derive your A I layer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a77911831e662bfb60bf1482c53fd0bbfa23f315c2eeb4580e8d46b5d83eb469",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 2.229125,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 98
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Three \u2014 three tier context.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7bbf2b92bba05f4ee479244f92445b67bc476bd09bf75e4f43c2941f1dbebe23",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 1.6254166666666667,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 106
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Global, on demand, and ticket only.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9bf5ace59cd896cb1e48b0518604cd3bbb240d0fffc9c345e0e9fab090c6b607",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 1.9040416666666666,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 111
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Four \u2014 focused prime commands.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e108e13fad46636800bb2fc6497f56a5b804893c063c0ac77a12350559028d87",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 1.7182916666666668,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 117
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "One per slice.",
      "checksum": "sha256:780ed73b41ba211b66edd78ce862f46ce77c43a4e5de40a56031707945aea420",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 1.068125,
      "word_count": 3,
      "words_offset": 122
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Five \u2014 parallel worktrees.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2cfea06bd4d199144a2a186e41417b19e5f8684951c8d7aae992162b44bc399a",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 1.7182916666666668,
      "word_count": 4,
      "words_offset": 125
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Multiple agents, zero collisions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9dc37e37dc7f95ccb09e0cbebf6dd69a846113309ec7e54450bf500e39a02df5",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 1.9504583333333334,
      "word_count": 4,
      "words_offset": 129
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Six \u2014 size by coupling, not by line count.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0a64e527bc2cdd9ba810b819ffd73351938ea969a0d81f69efe84b02ae71b17a",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 2.3684166666666666,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 133
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "The most precious resource isn't your wallet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0b3751aff61cc4047dc453d08d84a10e8a886bee41c656eacb0b4b8068d2b547",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 2.275541666666667,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 142
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "It's the context.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f62c795a827ef4f5d5a0f140c7397ca9bfec49d6d4aaaafb266aea15ada16616",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 1.3003333333333333,
      "word_count": 3,
      "words_offset": 149
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Protect it like a finite tank.",
      "checksum": "sha256:261abbef64ea5d5ae9875c5f7d72639d21924da1f1fe4a990bb15d7ccd1ef890",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 1.6718333333333333,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 152
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "So \u2014 vertical slices, or shared test folders.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0013fc4afbee34bf03656893b30ef0324ce146b6fd011125353d7b6245dcb0a3",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 2.6935,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 158
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Which one are you running?",
      "checksum": "sha256:698681d08c23bd9ec178bfc22bc9a9e6c643a9c98fa01ba2499f72721a35ef5a",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 1.253875,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 166
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "Drop your take.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c5eb8595f8239a64f295f8c78892427d5661c18e7bf9a4e81a3dedc98989db8a",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 1.0216666666666667,
      "word_count": 3,
      "words_offset": 171
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "And if you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous dot AI community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d01d802f811b1fc829c7edcfab600abdc85092a91ad7b50fb667392cbe5b394b",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 4.226041666666666,
